               <p>Q. Did you go up when the last witness had hold of the prisoner - A. I did, the hemp was laying at his feet.</p>
               <p>Q. Whose was it - 
               <persName id="t18110710-39-person387">A. Joseph Watson</persName>
            's; I had the hemp and the prisoner taken back to the wharf. This is the hemp, it is worth nine or ten shillings.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was in liquor when I did it.</p>
